#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn11.20"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn11.20:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 11 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 11 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn11.20:0.2"
msgid "2. Dutiyavagga "
msgstr "2. The Second Chapter "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 20. Saṅghavandanāsutta → tatiyasakkanamassanasuttaṃ (bj, s2, s3) | sakkanamassanasuttaṃ (3) (s1) | sakka-namassana (3) (pts1)
msgctxt "sn11.20:0.3"
msgid "20. Saṅghavandanāsutta "
msgstr "20. Who Sakka Worships "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts1ed1.236, pts2ed1.506, sc1
msgctxt "sn11.20:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthiyaṃ jetavane. "
msgstr "Near Sāvatthī in Jeta’s Grove. "

msgctxt "sn11.20:1.2"
msgid "Tatra kho … pe … etadavoca: "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn11.20:1.3"
msgid "“bhūtapubbaṃ, bhikkhave, sakko devānamindo mātaliṃ saṅgāhakaṃ āmantesi: "
msgstr "“Once upon a time, mendicants, Sakka, lord of gods, addressed his charioteer Mātali, "

msgctxt "sn11.20:1.4"
msgid "‘yojehi, samma mātali, sahassayuttaṃ ājaññarathaṃ, uyyānabhūmiṃ gacchāma subhūmiṃ dassanāyā’ti. "
msgstr "‘My dear Mātali, harness the chariot with its team of a thousand thoroughbreds. We will go to a park and see the scenery.’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn11.20:1.5"
msgid "‘Evaṃ, bhaddantavā’ti kho, bhikkhave, mātali saṅgāhako sakkassa devānamindassa paṭissutvā, sahassayuttaṃ ājaññarathaṃ yojetvā sakkassa devānamindassa paṭivedesi: "
msgstr "‘Yes, lord,’ replied Mātali. He harnessed the chariot and informed Sakka, "

msgctxt "sn11.20:1.6"
msgid "‘yutto kho te, mārisa, sahassayutto ājaññaratho, "
msgstr "‘Good sir, the chariot with its team of a thousand thoroughbreds has been harnessed. "

msgctxt "sn11.20:1.7"
msgid "yassadāni kālaṃ maññasī’ti."
msgstr "Please go at your convenience.’"

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn11.20:1.8"
msgid "Atha kho, bhikkhave, sakko devānamindo vejayantapāsādā orohanto añjaliṃ katvā sudaṃ bhikkhusaṃghaṃ namassati. "
msgstr "Then Sakka descended from the Palace of Victory, raised his joined palms, and revered the mendicant Saṅgha. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn11.20:1.9"
msgid "Atha kho, bhikkhave, mātali saṅgāhako sakkaṃ devānamindaṃ gāthāya ajjhabhāsi: "
msgstr "So Mātali the charioteer addressed Sakka in verse: "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn11.20:2.1"
msgid "‘Tañhi ete namasseyyuṃ, "
msgstr "‘It’s these who should worship you, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn11.20:2.2"
msgid "pūtidehasayā narā; "
msgstr "namely the humans stuck in their putrid bodies, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn11.20:2.3"
msgid "Nimuggā kuṇapamhete, "
msgstr "sunk in a corpse, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn11.20:2.4"
msgid "khuppipāsasamappitā. "
msgstr "stricken by hunger and thirst. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "sn11.20:3.1"
msgid "Kiṃ nu tesaṃ pihayasi, "
msgstr "Why then do you envy those "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn11.20:3.2"
msgid "anāgārāna vāsava; "
msgstr "who are homeless, Vāsava? "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn11.20:3.3"
msgid "Ācāraṃ isinaṃ brūhi, "
msgstr "Relate the hermits’ way of life, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn11.20:3.4"
msgid "taṃ suṇoma vaco tavā’ti. "
msgstr "let us hear what you have to say.’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts2ed1.507, sc4
msgctxt "sn11.20:4.1"
msgid "‘Etaṃ tesaṃ pihayāmi, "
msgstr "‘This is why I envy the "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn11.20:4.2"
msgid "anāgārāna mātali; "
msgstr "homeless, Mātali. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn11.20:4.3"
msgid "Yamhā gāmā pakkamanti, "
msgstr "When they leave a village, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn11.20:4.4"
msgid "anapekkhā vajanti te. "
msgstr "they go without concern. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "sn11.20:5.1"
msgid "Na tesaṃ koṭṭhe openti, "
msgstr "They hoard no goods in storerooms, "

#. HTML: <br>
#. VAR: kumbhi → kumbhe (bj) | kumbhā (s1-3, km, pts1, mr) | kumbhī (pts2)
#. VAR: kaḷopiyaṃ → khalopiyaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "sn11.20:5.2"
msgid "na kumbhi na kaḷopiyaṃ; "
msgstr "nor in pots or baskets. "

#. HTML: <br>
#. VAR: Paraniṭṭhitamesānā → paraniṭṭhitamesanā (s1-3, km, mr)
msgctxt "sn11.20:5.3"
msgid "Paraniṭṭhitamesānā, "
msgstr "They seek food prepared by others, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn11.20:5.4"
msgid "tena yāpenti subbatā. "
msgstr "and, true to their vows, live on that. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc6
msgctxt "sn11.20:6.1"
msgid "Sumantamantino dhīrā, "
msgstr "The wise whose words are full of wisdom, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn11.20:6.2"
msgid "tuṇhībhūtā samañcarā; "
msgstr "live peacefully and quietly. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn11.20:6.3"
msgid "Devā viruddhā asurehi, "
msgstr "Gods fight with demons, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn11.20:6.4"
msgid "puthu maccā ca mātali. "
msgstr "and mortals fight each other, Mātali. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc7
msgctxt "sn11.20:7.1"
msgid "Aviruddhā viruddhesu, "
msgstr "Not fighting among those who fight, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn11.20:7.2"
msgid "attadaṇḍesu nibbutā; "
msgstr "they’re extinguished among those who’ve taken up arms. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn11.20:7.3"
msgid "Sādānesu anādānā, "
msgstr "Not grasping among those who grasp, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn11.20:7.4"
msgid "te namassāmi mātalī’ti. "
msgstr "they’re who I worship, Mātali.’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc8
msgctxt "sn11.20:8.1"
msgid "‘Seṭṭhā hi kira lokasmiṃ, "
msgstr "‘Those who you worship "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn11.20:8.2"
msgid "ye tvaṃ sakka namassasi; "
msgstr "seem to be the best in the world, Sakka. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn11.20:8.3"
msgid "Ahampi te namassāmi, "
msgstr "I too will worship "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn11.20:8.4"
msgid "ye namassasi vāsavā’”ti. "
msgstr "those who you worship, Vāsava.’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts2ed1.508, sc9
msgctxt "sn11.20:9.1"
msgid "Idaṃ vatvāna maghavā, "
msgstr "After saying this, Maghavā the chief, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn11.20:9.2"
msgid "devarājā sujampati; "
msgstr "king of gods, Sujā’s husband, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn11.20:9.3"
msgid "Bhikkhusaṅghaṃ namassitvā, "
msgstr "having worshipped the mendicant Saṅgha, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn11.20:9.4"
msgid "pamukho rathamāruhīti. "
msgstr "climbed into his chariot.” "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn11.20:9.5"
msgid "Dutiyo vaggo. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. REF: sc10
#. VAR: pana → vatapadena (bj, s1-3, km, pts2)
msgctxt "sn11.20:10.1"
msgid "Devā pana tayo vuttā, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn11.20:10.2"
msgid "daliddañca rāmaṇeyyakaṃ; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn11.20:10.3"
msgid "Yajamānañca vandanā, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn11.20:10.4"
msgid "tayo sakkanamassanāti. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></blockquote></article></section></body></html>
